{"tid":2188093,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無讀過U 既人可以話比我知點解雪係白色？","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T05:05:52.000Z","uid":364705,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ec5c823f82cc9be0f2a964445f8b39a3737eeb","tid":2188093,"uid":364705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"而唔是其他色？"},{"pid":"cd63e3994eba5f0ce000ad8be0cc1062b1518b5f","tid":2188093,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"含到雪雪聲之後噴出黎既係白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee60898ce711cf2591bb860aa797c7601c13a9ff","tid":2188093,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"恒大冇教"},{"pid":"962937b0d03932f2e73a5ce3cf4c7a034f6d6cd9","tid":2188093,"uid":25367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYHMufFvXBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnYHMufFvXBQ&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=39f2d1aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYHMufFvXBQ</a><br />\n等c.c.答你"},{"pid":"ab1d6c000664df7082f0fecb06f114214315d961","tid":2188093,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"問C.C."},{"pid":"cc7f9714ec0af98026f9576e354606f086ed8abd","tid":2188093,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"這一切與空氣有關。一個物體通過「吸收」或「反射」特定波長的光來獲得其顏色。比如一個蘋果會呈現紅色，是因為它吸收所有顏色除了紅色，並反射回到我們的眼睛。這就是為什麼我們會看到一個紅色的蘋果。<br />\n<br />\n白色物體可以反射所有光線，雪花是冰晶與空氣分子的混合物。雪是由大量的冰晶組成的，隨着形成晶體的複雜形狀，雪累積在一起導致多個晶體彎曲，它們之間的間隙發生光的反射或折射，這導致光被散射。最終所有波長的光被反射出來，就讓雪變成了白色，有時是藍色。雪呈現白色的原因與一堆玻璃碎片看上去是白色的原因是一樣的。"},{"pid":"aff7b7ed88d1bd05bddc0539525215ec3bf11d55","tid":2188093,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"962937b0d